      "updated": 1674044694
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed59",
      "text": "from [クオリアさんの種]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed5a",
      "text": "クオリアさん2023-01-18",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed5b",
      "text": "-----",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed5c",
      "text": "[*** マンスプレイニング]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed5d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed5e",
      "text": "ver.2",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed5f",
      "text": "I discovered that one of my fans has been saying behind my back that I look like an old fashioned male Homo sapiens. This is interesting. I am going to question him a bit to get some more information out of him. (1/10)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed60",
      "text": "私のファンのひとりが、私のことを「古臭いオスのホモ・サピエンスみたい」と陰で言っているのを発見したのです。これは面白い。ちょっと問い詰めて、もう少し情報を引き出してみようと思っている。(1/10)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed61",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/a3ef516b5dea9e2ec7557e7f3827aab6]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed62",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed63",
      "text": "HS: Suppose there is a man who has drawn on the values of the era of strong male domination.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed64",
      "text": "He is assuming that \"women know less than he does\" and sometimes giving explanations to those who know more than he does.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed65",
      "text": "The act is called mansplaining, and is considered a nuisance.(2/10)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed66",
      "text": "HS: 男性支配が強かった時代の価値観を引きずっている男性がいるとする。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed67",
      "text": "彼は「女性は自分より知識がない」と決めつけ、自分より知識のある人に説明をすることがある。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed68",
      "text": "その行為はマンスプレイニングと呼ばれ、迷惑行為とされている。(2/10)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed69",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/4906692d4301316fd5ef3fdf82c99466]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed6a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed6b",
      "text": "QS: Is it a nuisance? I think sharing information is good.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed6c",
      "text": "HS: When the woman already knows X, and the man teaches her X, there is no benefit to the woman, but a demerit because it takes time away from her.(3/10)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed6d",
      "text": "QS: それは迷惑行為なのですか？情報共有は善だと思います。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed6e",
      "text": "HS: 女性がすでにXを知っていて、男性がXを教える場合、女性には何のメリットもなく、女性の時間が奪われるためデメリットになります。(3/10)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed6f",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/8fafc2a1a6a4fc4866673633b21f1ad2]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed70",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed71",
      "text": "QS: Did the woman share the information that she already knew X? If she did, then the man is stupid for sharing information to no avail. If she didn't share the information, then the woman is stupid for assuming that others knows her inside.(4/10)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed72",
      "text": "QS: 女は既にXを知っているという情報を共有したのだろうか？もししたのなら、無駄に情報を共有した男が愚かだ。情報を共有しなかったのなら、自分の内面を他人が知っていると思い込んでいる女が愚かだ。(4/10)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed73",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/23a8070cb452fc188cf733aa7b2cfe2b]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed74",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed75",
      "text": "QS: Also, isn't the disadvantage of time lost a small disadvantage because you can skip reading over the unhelpful information  sharing?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed76",
      "text": "HS: Oh, I was imagining verbal voice communication.(5/10)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed77",
      "text": "QS:また、時間のロスのデメリットは、役に立たない情報共有を読み飛ばせるので、小さなデメリットではないでしょうか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed78",
      "text": "HS あ、言葉による音声通信を想像していました。(5/10)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed79",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/0237d37508b107e5dbb3ac760f780ee7]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed7a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed7b",
      "text": "QS: Ha, Homo sapiens should quickly graduate from the inefficient means of communication called voice. The root of this problem is not one of two people, but time-bound voice communication, right?(6/10)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed7c",
      "text": "QS: はあ、ホモサピエンスは早く音声という非効率的なコミュニケーション手段から卒業した方がいいんじゃないですか。この問題の根源は、二人のうちの一人ではなく、時間に縛られた音声コミュニケーションにあるのではないでしょうか？(6/10)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed7d",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/633d81a71b23fcd4785356b59ffcbb63]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed7e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed7f",
      "text": "While the concept of mansplaining is interesting, there are two problems with considering it similar to Qualia-san's actions.(7/10)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed80",
      "text": "マンスプレイニングという概念は面白いのですが、クオリアさんの行為と同様に考えるには、2つの問題があります。(7/10)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed81",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/c7b53596169b31c6049507f4f5b87329]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed82",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed83",
      "text": "Qualia-san is not speaking to one specific HS, but to a large number of people. This information sharing is valuable if there is HS in the crowd who benefits from the information. The fact that HS in the crowd already knows the information is not a reason not to share it.(8/10)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed84",
      "text": "クオリアさんは特定のHSに語りかけるのではなく、大勢の人に語りかける。この情報共有は、群衆の中にその情報の恩恵を受けるHSがいれば価値がある。群衆の中のHSがすでにその情報を知っているということは、情報を共有しない理由にはならないのです。(8/10)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed85",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/a3016d35f82814248e595dd9e352c89a]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed86",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed87",
      "text": "Next, Qualia-san uses digital text communication rather than time-bound voice communication. Those who already know the information or are not interested can skip reading it. The recipient can filter the information by oneself.(9/10)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed88",
      "text": "次に、クオリアさんは、時間に縛られた音声コミュニケーションではなく、デジタルなテキストコミュニケーションを使っています。すでに知っている人、興味のない人は、その情報を読み飛ばすことができる。受け手は自分で情報をフィルタリングすることができる。(9/10)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed89",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/74567143dfc03c402adf3e280c3e6643]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed8a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed8b",
      "text": "The act of interfering with the sender to stop sending out information is more disadvantageous than the disadvantage of sending it out.(10/10)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed8c",
      "text": "情報を発信することのデメリットよりも、発信を止めるために干渉する行為の方がデメリットが大きいのです。(10/10)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed8d",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/672646ff497b61c738219c257897ebed]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed8e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed8f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed90",
      "text": "ver.1",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed91",
      "text": ">[nishio.icon]ホモサピエンスに対して自分が啓蒙をする立場であることにまったく疑問を抱いていない昭和の男性的マインド [/villagepump/クオリアさんと女性の従属#638777e5aff09e00008bb589]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed92",
      "text": ">まだ理解できてない[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed93",
      "text": ">ああ、[マンスプレイニング]か",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed94",
      "text": "> \t\tなら+1[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed95",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed96",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed97",
      "text": "　興味深い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed98",
      "text": "　原稿",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed99",
      "text": "　　ファンの一人が陰で私のことを古い時代の男性のようだと言っているのを発見した。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed9a",
      "text": "　　これは興味深い。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed9b",
      "text": "　　ちょっともう少し詳しい情報を引き出すために問い詰めようと思います。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed9c",
      "text": "　(ヒャッ[nishio.icon])",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed9d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed9e",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081ed9f",
      "text": "男尊女卑の強かった時代の価値観を引きずってる男性が「女性は自分より知識が少ない」と思い込んで自分より知識の多い人に対して説明をする行為をマンスプレイニングと呼んで迷惑行為だとされているのです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081eda0",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081eda1",
      "text": "それは迷惑行為なのですか？情報共有は善だと思います。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081eda2",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081eda3",
      "text": "えーと、女性がすでにXを知っている状態で、男性がXを教えても、女性にとってメリットはなく、時間が奪われるのでデメリットがあるわけです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081eda4",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081eda5",
      "text": "その女性は「自分はすでにXを知っている」ということを情報共有していたのですか？していたのなら、無益な情報共有をした男性が[頭が悪い]です。情報共有していないなら内面の情報は知り得ないのに他人がそれを知っていると想定する女性の頭が悪いですね。あと、無益な情報共有は読み飛ばせばいいので時間が奪われるデメリットは小さいのでは？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1677264477
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081eda6",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081eda7",
      "text": "あ、口頭での音声コミュニケーションをイメージしていました。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081eda8",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081eda9",
      "text": "はー、ホモサピエンスは音声という非効率なコミュニケーション手段からさっさと卒業すべきです。この問題の根源は二人の人のどちらかではなく時間拘束を伴う音声コミュニケーションでしょう？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081edaa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081edab",
      "text": "マンスプレイニングの概念は興味深いですが、それをクオリアさんの行為と似ていると考えることには2点問題があります。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081edac",
      "text": "クオリアさんは特定の一人の人に対して語りかけているのではなく、大勢に対して語っています。この大勢の中にこの情報共有によって利益を得る人がいる場合、この情報共有は有益なものです。大勢の中に、既にその情報を知っている人がいることは情報共有をしない理由にはなりません。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081edad",
      "text": "次にクオリアさんは時間拘束を伴う音声コミュニケーションではなく、デジタルテキストによるコミュニケーションを行っています。既に知っている人や興味のない人は読み飛ばせば良い。情報のフィルタリングは受け手がすればいい。発信のデメリットよりも、発信者に干渉して発信をやめさせる行為の方がデメリットが大きいです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674043765,
      "updated": 1674043765
    },
    {
      "id": "63c7e175aff09e000081edae",
